      "rationale": "Test conditions were drawn from the observational clinical dataset rather than a controlled laboratory protocol. Operating conditions were inferred from device telemetry, introducing confounding from patient physiology, medication, and device wear state. Achieved level 2 against required level 5; this is the primary gap driving the Not-accepted recommendation in the base COU, though the assessment team here argues the observational breadth compensates."
    },
    {
