      "rationale": "R²=0.81 reported as primary comparison metric. Point-by-point E_rel computed at four of five operating points; fifth operating point had insufficient patient data. Uncertainty propagation applied to regression but not to individual operating-point comparisons. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
