      "rationale": "NIH is the direct clinical hemolysis metric specified in the COU. The observational dataset reports NIH derived from pfHb measurements using the standard Heuser-Opitz formula, which is the accepted transformation. QoI relevance is high; achieved level 4 equals required level 4."
